item.description: Welcome I am a Ph.D. student in Distributed and Intelligent Computing Lab at the Electrical Engineering and Computer Science (EECS) Department, University of Missouri, under the supervision of Professor Yi Shang. I obtained my M.S. degree in Computer Science at University of Missouri as well, and obtained my B.S. degree in Software Engineering at Beijing Jiaotong University. My research interests include Deep Learning, Artificial Intelligence, Computational Biology, Big Data, etc.
